msgctxt "56_Owner"
msgid "Hi, welcome! Ah, if it isn't Akiyama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68_Akiyama"
msgid "Hi there. I think you got a call from Hana-chan, right? So\\r\n"
"how did Shoko-san do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80_Owner"
msgid "I have some great tuna today, so I recommended the otoro.\\r\n"
"But wouldn't you know it? All she ate was the daily special\\r\n"
"before going on her way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "How much is the special?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104_Owner"
msgid "980 yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "Wow, cheap! Can I have one?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128_Owner"
msgid "All sold out, I'm afraid. But, you know, she was a little\\r\n"
"off today. She usually only eats uni, awabi－you know, the\\r\n"
"pricey stuff. What's going on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "Hmm. So I guess she hasn't touched that million yen, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152_Owner"
msgid "Wait, what? When Hana-chan told me to make her spend\\r\n"
"money... Hey, is this another one of your tests?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "Something like that. Thanks for your help. I'll have to drop\\r\n"
"by again soon."
msgstr ""

